{"tid":1909641,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"滯留湖北港人準備乘包機回港   難淹興奮車上自拍","createTime":"2020-03-04T06:04:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T12:42:56.000Z","uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"0e0639f365e16f1f3feb1b7fa8186f038850b10e","tid":1909641,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T06:04:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1RkqZpc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1RkqZpc.png&h=11b1ac07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=382950\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D382950&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeIWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=195c8b3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D382950&h=43fa5651\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=382950</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】有滯留湖北的港人陸續登上當地政府安排的專車，離開所屬小區前往機場。<br />\n<br />\n早上近九時，有身穿保護衣的人員，開車到武漢市內不同的小區，接載包機名單上的港人。<br />\n<br />\n有上車的港人穿上由當地小區提供的保護衣，並戴上眼罩、口罩及手套。<br />\n<br />\n這輛專車由省外事辦安排，分別去七個不同地點接送他們到武漢機場。<br />\n<br />\n終於可以返香港，她們難掩興奮的心情，不時在車上交談及自拍。<br />\n<br />\n沿途所見，馬路上有多個公安檢查站，專車去到機場高速公路收費站，所有人都要出示證件。由於公安未有收到放行通知，她們被迫在收費站口等待，按計劃她們在下午約兩時乘坐港府首班包機返港。"},{"pid":"ffa8bd9e5d6e251c045301fe2c686ec8ee7f3b0b","tid":1909641,"uid":61604,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0e0639f365e16f1f3feb1b7fa8186f038850b10e","tid":1909641,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T06:04:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj